{
  "stem": "214.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the nun, the one sister so and so, she came up, and she says, why are you not going to work?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we tell her-- we told the Sister Emma [SPEAKING GERMAN] You understand?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, you know, you never heard that the war is over for us?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and those Americans, you know, they were really unprepared for all those slave laborers, and they didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, there were Poles who were working in the fields there, and we knew-- some of them were our best friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] And so we-- we just-- maybe for a week or two, we were just sitting there, going down, taking food, coming back up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- we-- we didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For all we knew at that time, we might have been the only three Jewish-- five Jewish people left.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, we-- we were totally cut off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's really, it's funny when you think of it now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody-- nobody in Weinsberg, nobody ever-- nobody ever knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, what happened, the Americans, there was some, I mean, captain, who, he took over, and they started organizing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there were nationalities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were Poles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were Italians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were-- I mean, all the nationalities as slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they found themselves with so many people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a-- there were big barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a base where the Germans kept POWs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think American-- not American.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "English and French POWs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when-- before the Americans came, they shipped them all out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So those barracks were empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
